	<item>
		<title>最近买的书（书单）</title>
		<link>http://hzh.me/2011/11/03/books/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 03 Nov 2011 11:38:38 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>dinohu</dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://hzh.me/?p=247</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[最近几家商家分别做活动，便宜了我们这些人，我以前是不怎么喜欢看书的，不过价格太诱惑，还是忍不住买了十几本，估计够我几年看的了。

&nbsp;

先是京东的活动，满<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">200</span>减半，凑了半天单凑了<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">200</span>零几块钱，用一年的钱买打折的正版书还是很合算的。这些书里我只想要两本的，布什传和乔不什传，如果前两天买也要花<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">100</span>块，这次正好，其它的书等于白送了，书单如下：

&nbsp;

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">1.30</span>年后，你拿什么养活自己？顶级理财师给上班族的财富人生规划课<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">2.</span>淡定的人生不寂寞<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">3.</span>林徽因传：你若安好便是晴天（附林徽因诗歌选和林徽因年谱）<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">4.</span>史蒂夫<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">·</span>乔布斯传（<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Steve Jobs</span>：<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">A Biography</span>乔布斯唯一正式授权传记简体中文版）<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">5.</span>去，你的旅行<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">6.</span>抉择时刻：乔治<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">·</span>沃克<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">·</span>布什自传（精装本）<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">7.</span>说服力<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">8.</span>人脉是设计出来的

&nbsp;

前两天苏宁就在做活动了，当时我没注意，刚好我想买个热水器也要花个几百块钱，苏宁正好是买多少送多少，算零元买书了，从下午吃完饭就回来凑才凑够了<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">300</span>块，苏宁的书实在太少了。书单如下：

&nbsp;

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">1.</span>品悟南怀瑾<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">.</span>国学的真意<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">2.</span>西方文明简史<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">(</span>第四版<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">)</span>上<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">.</span>下<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">3.</span>民国的角落<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">4.</span>对我影响最大的几本书<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">5.</span>解密曾国藩做人性格绝学<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">6.</span>民国风度<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">7.</span>周易今注今译<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">8.</span>国学常识一本通<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">9.</span>曾国藩家书<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">10.</span>历史不忍细看<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">-</span>黄文山读史

&nbsp;

今年买的书真还不少了，算上上次京东<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">618</span>活动，买了有<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">20</span>多本书，再加上前天院里又送了两本，可是到现在也就才看了两本，剩下的日子要加油了，否则真对不花掉的这些钱。

<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"> </span>

&nbsp;]]></content:encoded>
