<img class="aligncenter" title="k3g2" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-p4cVlatnqSY/TtTBNq6hyEI/AAAAAAAAAeU/zWzl7JpEPuI/s640/DSCF3343.JPG" alt="" width="640" height="480" />

白色广告版 kindle3 3g

<a href="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-iCxrJCslRvI/TtTBOjEUh7I/AAAAAAAAAeg/YlEVyMXN5IM/s640/DSCF3344.JPG"><img class="aligncenter" title="k33g1" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-iCxrJCslRvI/TtTBOjEUh7I/AAAAAAAAAeg/YlEVyMXN5IM/s640/DSCF3344.JPG" alt="" width="640" height="480" /></a>

&nbsp;

kindle fire 出箱

<img class="aligncenter" title="kf1" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-wxplIkG4mhM/TtTBTKiY57I/AAAAAAAAAew/5gqdhZhxN10/s640/DSCF3345.JPG" alt="" width="640" height="480" />

