<img class="aligncenter" title="kf2" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-LU4uCHMDzGU/TtTBQ5XAsHI/AAAAAAAAAeo/PKOmakeoUwk/s640/DSCF3346.JPG" alt="" width="640" height="480" />

白色广告版 kindle3 3g开机，好漂亮

<img class="aligncenter" title="k33gopen" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-YFyuV_CH6N4/TtTBUNX0f1I/AAAAAAAAAe4/0lBq4SeCNVw/s640/DSCF3347.JPG" alt="" width="640" height="480" />

