kindle fire和ipad2放一起，小了一半

<img class="aligncenter" title="kfipad" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-vTnMcvf8pBI/TtTBgXM5z6I/AAAAAAAAAfk/scp_anNR8IU/s640/DSCF3352.JPG" alt="" width="640" height="480" />

&nbsp;

<img class="aligncenter" title="kfipad" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-he51lLE3EOE/TtTBhW18LGI/AAAAAAAAAfs/sqLZfBYltQw/s640/DSCF3353.JPG" alt="" width="640" height="480" />

&nbsp;

imdb

<img class="aligncenter" title="soft_imdb" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-LnGqWQSaZuI/TtTBicTFv6I/AAAAAAAAAf0/bukVNMkfSt0/s640/DSCF3354.JPG" alt="" width="640" height="480" />

